        </div>
        <div class="message sent"><small>TX · 14:32:05.311</small><code>01 03 00 01 00 01 D5 CA</code></div>
      </div>

      <div class="composer">
        <div class="composer-tools"><span>HEX</span><span>UTF-8</span><span>⌘ Enter to send</span></div>
        <div class="composer-input"><code>01 03 00 02 00 02</code><button aria-label="Send message">↑</button></div>
